These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-6-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water
House: futuristic, palace
The people have 2 different jobs:  photographer, police-officer
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, malaysian
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, animation
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, tennis
City: berlin, london
1. the palace house is not the police-officer##6
2. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
3. the italian is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
5. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
6. the photographer is the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Beverage      | water   | hot-chocolate |
| Hobby         | palace | futuristic       |
| Music-Genre   | photographer | police-officer       |
| Nationality   | italian | malaysian     |
| Pet           | thriller    | animation         |
| Sport         | cricket | tennis        |
| Transport     | berlin | london         |

