2. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the japanese##1
3. the lawyer is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
4. the fonseca-smoker is not the person who's sport is cricket##6
5. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | japanese | indian  |
| Hobby         | cain   | fonseca |
| Job           | lawyer  | paramedic |
| Movie-Genre   | cricket  | tennis    |
| Music-Genre   | pop     | ambient   |
| Pet           | mah-jongg  | monopoly      |
| Transport     | scooter | quad-bike |

